<div class="title">Trip of a Life Time</div>
<div class="substance">DOM & Amphetamine (Adderall)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Rob+Bader&Exact=1">Rob Bader</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Rob Bader. "Trip of a Life Time: An Experience with DOM & Amphetamine (Adderall) (exp4303)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Dec 21, 2000. erowid.org/exp/4303</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
